reviews.review_text:
a barely listenable show now sounds great came across this one a while back after discovering the weird and unique WRS with Fierro. the horns provide a sweet and sad tone under this WRS and i'm so glad to have it in good quality now!

this show could use some noise reduction therapy but I understand the preservation of fidelity is more important for most. time to run this one thru audacity's noise reduction feature and dig in.

thanks as always mr miller!!
